query:
INSERT INTO submissions (exchange_id, link, submitter, submitted_at)
                    VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
                    ON CONFLICT (exchange_id, submitter) DO UPDATE SET link = $2
                    RETURNING 
                        id AS "id!", 
                        exchange_id AS "exchange_id!",
                        link AS "link!",
                        submitter AS "submitter!",
                        submitted_at AS "submitted_at!"
